                                                     <span id="dgPanelHistory_ctl02_Label1"><b>05 Mar 2014</b></span>
                                                </td><td title="Link to panel" align="left" valign="middle" width="70%">
																	<a id="dgPanelHistory_ctl02_lnkPanelName" href="NGBOViewPanel.aspx?PanelId=1-1R46YN">EPSRC Equipment Business Case - March 2014</a>
																	
												</td><td valign="middle">
